snippet: Padraig Harrington recorded the lowest official score of his life, a 10-under-par 61 to set a course record in the Transitions Championship in Palm Harbor, Fla.
abstract: Padraig Harrington takes first-round lead at Transitions Championship golf tournament; other golf news noted.
